caption:
Cranford is so lucky to have a spot like The Garrison take over the Kilkenny House location! 

Today I met @fo0odforfun for some after work drinks and I am so mad at myself for not stopping in sooner. You can sit at the bar or at a table and order drinks and pay directly from your phone. It’s so easy and the service is wonderful. 

I tried “The Eastside” and the “Hello Cranford”. The Eastside is made from my favorite gin Hendricks, lime, simple syrup, cucumber, and mint! The “Hello Cranford” was sooo good and  made with Tito’s, St. Germain, lemon juice, grapefruit, and soda. The name is too cute!

This is such a great place to stop in for a great cocktail or glass of wine. They also have great food options like pizza and small plates because they are owned by the fabulous @wonder !!! 

If you haven’t been yet, stop in soon! 
.
.
.
